FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782910143
OL,3,CMaternity inquiry chair disappointed
OL,4,Cby 'defensive' Oxford University
OL,5,CHospitals
OL,7,FThe Labour peer said she was
OL,8,F"extremely concerned" by the "lack of
OL,9,Fbasic care" at the John Radcliffe
OL,10,FHospital, Oxford, and Horton General
OL,11,FHospital, Banbury.
OL,13,FHer report also detailed concerns from
OL,14,Fpatients and staff about a dominant
OL,15,Fculture within the trust of doing
OL,16,Fthings the 'Oxford way', which could
OL,17,Fsuppress debate and be used as a
OL,18,Freason for refusing patient requests.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@UO]pD@^OUqD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782910143
OL,3,CMaternity inquiry chair disappointed
OL,4,Cby 'defensive' Oxford University
OL,5,CHospitals
OL,7,FBaroness Amos told ITV News Meridian:
OL,8,F"I have been very disappointed by the
OL,9,Fresponse that we got from (Oxford
OL,10,FUniversity Hospitals) in relation to
OL,11,Fwhat we fed back through our report.
OL,13,F"We talked to a lot of families. This
OL,14,Fissue of "this is the Oxford way"`
OL,15,FOxford as a city, with a university
OL,16,Fwhich is considered to be world-class.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@[pmrD@UpnuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782910143
OL,3,CMaternity inquiry chair disappointed
OL,4,Cby 'defensive' Oxford University
OL,5,CHospitals
OL,7,F"Yet, what we found in this trust was
OL,8,Fa lack of basic care. It's extremely
OL,9,Fconcerning. I think it's important
OL,10,Fthat the trust's leadership take on
OL,11,Fboard what the families have said, but
OL,12,Falso take on board what their own
OL,13,Fstaff have said."
OL,15,FOxford University Hospitals has
OL,16,Fapologised unreservedly and committed
OL,17,Fto "listen harder, act faster, and
OL,18,Fhold ourselves accountable for the
OL,19,Fimprovements that women, babies,
OL,20,Ffamilies and staff have every right to
OL,21,Fexpect."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@QO]yD@DOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782910143
OL,3,CMaternity inquiry chair disappointed
OL,4,Cby 'defensive' Oxford University
OL,5,CHospitals
OL,7,FAsked if the trust leadership took the
OL,8,Fissues raised by her report seriously
OL,9,Fenough, Baroness Amos said: "My sense
OL,10,Fis that given the culture change
OL,11,Frequired, the importance of
OL,12,Finterrogating exactly what is going on
OL,13,F` the response feels defensive rather
OL,14,Fthan one where there is a sense of:
OL,15,F'If this is what our staff and our
OL,16,Ffamilies are saying back to us, what
OL,17,Fcan we do about it?'"
OL,26,@qD@]OUyD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782910143
OL,3,CMaternity inquiry chair disappointed
OL,4,Cby 'defensive' Oxford University
OL,5,CHospitals
OL,7,FThe Oxford report was part of the
OL,8,Ffinal reports published by the
OL,9,Findependent National Maternity and
OL,10,FNeonatal Investigation, which also
OL,11,Fexamined maternity care at University
OL,12,FHospitals Sussex and East Kent
OL,13,FHospitals.
OL,15,FThe Amos report into OUH noted: "We
OL,16,Ffound that the senior leadership team
OL,17,Fhad a limited insight into how
OL,18,Foperational challenges impacted on the
OL,19,Fstress staff experienced."
OL,26,@wD@aOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782910143
OL,3,CMaternity inquiry chair disappointed
OL,4,Cby 'defensive' Oxford University
OL,5,CHospitals
OL,7,FIn a statement, Oxford University
OL,8,FHospitals' Interim Chief Executive
OL,9,FSimon Crowther said: "We apologise
OL,10,Funreservedly to the women, babies and
OL,11,Ffamilies who suffered in our care, or
OL,12,Fwhose experience caused them grief or
OL,13,Fdistress. We failed them at some of
OL,14,Fthe most important and vulnerable
OL,15,Fmoments of their lives.
OL,17,F"We accept what families have told the
OL,18,Finvestigation, the failings in care
OL,19,Fthey describe in the report, and our
OL,20,Fresponsibility to act.
OL,26,@qD@VOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782910143
OL,3,CMaternity inquiry chair disappointed
OL,4,Cby 'defensive' Oxford University
OL,5,CHospitals
OL,7,F"The report also reflects what many of
OL,8,Four staff told the investigation. They
OL,9,Fdescribed people who are committed to
OL,10,Fdoing their best for women, babies and
OL,11,Ffamilies, often in difficult and
OL,12,Fdemanding circumstances. We are sorry
OL,13,Ffor the toll this has taken on them,
OL,14,Fand we thank them for their dedication
OL,15,Fto the families in their care.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782910143
OL,3,CMaternity inquiry chair disappointed
OL,4,Cby 'defensive' Oxford University
OL,5,CHospitals
OL,7,FWe know that families' trust and
OL,8,Fconfidence in our maternity services
OL,9,Fhave been badly damaged. We also know
OL,10,Fthey will not be rebuilt by words
OL,11,Falone, and that what matters now is
OL,12,Fwhat we do next."
OL,14,FThe Amos report's key recommendation
OL,15,Fwas that the government must appoint a
OL,16,Fnational maternity commissioner with
OL,17,Fthe legal powers to drive change in
OL,18,Forder to reduce harm to families.
OL,26,@tD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1782910143
OL,3,CMaternity inquiry chair disappointed
OL,4,Cby 'defensive' Oxford University
OL,5,CHospitals
OL,7,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,8,FCare has accepted that recommendation
OL,9,Fand plans to publish a national
OL,10,Fmaternity action plan in December 2026.
OL,12,FOxford University Hospitals NHS
OL,13,FFoundation Trust (OUH) has not
OL,14,Fresponded to a request by ITV News
OL,15,FMeridian to respond to Baroness Amos'
OL,16,Fspecific criticisms of the leadership
OL,17,Fteam.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/10
